Terminal Usage

Running Pytests:

‘py.test -s -v [repo_folder]/‘

Running A Singular Python Test Within Project Folder:

‘py.test [test_case].py’

Running A Singular Python Class Within Test Case:

‘py.test -q -s test_fixtures.py::TestClass’

Running A Singular Python Test Within Test Class:

‘py.test -q -s testcase.py::TestClassExample::test_example’

Append to any test:

-s: No capture. Don't suppress output.

-v: Verbose. Gimme all the info.

--tb=line: Shorten the tracebacks should an error occur.